# ITEMSET::GET_ITEMSET_SIZE

## Summary
Get the number of items in an item set

## Parameters
* **ITEMSET_INDEX** itemSet

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
If auto-cleaning, invalid items will get cleaned up first.
